{"tid":1468531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑警講大話] 2003 年立法會文件講明催淚彈會到期，冇最佳日期哩樣野","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:36:59.000Z","uid":1654,"like":102,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"eae863e2073356c7f816b19e80c1589de6701e91","tid":1468531,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200310/08/1008171.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200310%2F08%2F1008171.htm&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=4d8fe952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200310/08/1008171.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年時任保安局局長李少光回覆立法會<br />\n<br />\n主席女士：<br />\n<br />\n（一）早於二零零一年，警隊已手研究更換現有的防暴頭盔，以符合現時的國際安全標準。經過有關研究及試用過市場上各類頭盔後，警隊於二零零三年四月展開招標程序。<span style=\"color: red;\">此外，由於催淚彈有廠方訂明的儲存期限，所以警隊必須按照安全守則，購買新的彈藥以取代即將過期的存貨。</span>有關的招標程序已於二零零三年七月展開。"},{"pid":"d0ae1ff66f6093ed2cb1c33d920f9f8b2997c6cd","tid":1468531,"uid":135730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:06:46.000Z","msg":"死黑警今次你仲唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531760f15476c5d5cebf3b23a3815c3dc0dd5fb3","tid":1468531,"uid":117418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:07:57.000Z","msg":"推比記者聽日問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2576f2c1d3c5bad4d3bed43721666cabb327246","tid":1468531,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwWHyY2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwWHyY2.png&h=ccdb55e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f59e9a6eba5b87b